{"name": "dev-lxc", "metadata": {"name": "dev-lxc", "version": "0.2.0", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 4 - Beta", "Environment :: Console", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: POSIX :: Linux", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.10", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Topic :: Software Development"], "home_page": "https://github.com/Perfect5th/dev-lxc", "license": "MIT", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["PyYAML"], "summary": "A small wrapper for creating LXD system containers for development purposes.", "upload_time": 1732662586}, "documentation": ["# dev-lxc\n\nThis is a tidy little Python script I use when I want to quickly create an [LXD system container][1] for development purposes. It mounts the current directory in the home directory of the instance.\n\n## Installation\n\nIt's a single script file. Make sure you have [LXD installed][2] and Python 3.10 or higher. Get the file, make it executable, and put it on your `PATH` somewhere.\n\n## Basic Usage\n\n### Create an instance\n\nCreate an instance using a specific Ubuntu series, by codename:\n\n    dev_lxc create jammy\n\nThe instance name is generated from the current directory, so you can only have one instance of each series per directory. Names _will_ clash.\n\nIf you have a valid YAML file for configuring the instance (nice for if you want it to start with certain packages installed):\n\n    dev_lxc create jammy --config ./my-config.yaml\n\n### Open a shell in an instance\n\nOnce you've created an instance, you can spin up a shell in it:\n\n    dev_lxc shell jammy\n\nThe default user (`ubuntu`) should be uid-mapped to your user, so file permissions should be okay.\n\n### Exec a command in an instance\n\n    dev_lxc exec jammy 'echo \"hello\"'\n\nThis executes using `bash`, so try not to get too fancy. You can also provide environment variables:\n\n    dev_lxc exec jammy 'echo \"hello $MITCH\"' --env MITCH=\"mitchell\"\n\n### Stop or Start an instance\n\n    dev_lxc stop jammy\n\nStops the instance from running. Most other commands (`shell`, `exec`) should start the instance if it's stopped before running.\n\n    dev_lxc start jammy\n\nStarts it up again.\n\n### Remove Instance\n\n    dev_lxc remove jammy\n\nThis deletes the instance. It is gone for good.\n\n   [1]: https://canonical.com/lxd\n   [2]: https://canonical.com/lxd/install\n"], "modules": [{"name": "dev_lxc", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd", "documentation": ["!/usr/bin/env python3"], "functions": [{"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.create", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "config", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.shell", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "stop_after", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.remove", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.exec_cmd", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "command", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "stop_after", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "emphemeral", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "*env_args", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.start", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.stop", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd._exec_config", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "config", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Executes the `dev-lxc-exec` section of `config` in the container for `series`."]}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd._create_container", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "instance_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "series", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "config", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Creates a new container with the given `instance_name`."]}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd._get_status", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "instance_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Gets the current status of the dev container for `series`."]}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd._remove", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "instance_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd._start_if_stopped", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "instance_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Starts the LXD instance with name `instance_name` if it is not running.\n    "]}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd._stop", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "instance_name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.main", "asynchronous": false, "params": [], "returns": null, "documentation": []}], "variables": [{"name": "dev_lxc.cmd.PY_YAML", "type": null, "doc